The paper deals with algorithms for solving the shortest vector problem and the closest vector problem in the lattice, which are fundamental problems in computer science. The paper also introduces a new sieving procedure that significantly improves the running time of the algorithm for SVP in the $\ell_\infty$ norm. This suggests that the paper could belong to categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
